These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, peach, kiwi
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, accountant, entrepreneur
1. the person eating mango is in an even position##4
2. the videographer is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the videographer is the person eating peach##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
5. the accountant is the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | kiwi | mango | peach |
| Job    | accountant    | entrepreneur | videographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, fishing, card-games
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, jet-ski, ship
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | fishing | card-games | dancing |
| Transport   | ship    | jet-ski     | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, board-games, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, techno, ambient
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | writing     | board-games | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | techno | indie     | ambient  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, western, crime
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, parkour, swimming
1. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person watching drama movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | western  | drama  |
| Sport         | soccer  | parkour | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, fishing, filmmaking
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, polish, malaysian
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the italian##2
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
3. the malaysian is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | hiking   | filmmaking | fishing    |
| Nationality   | polish | malaysian     | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, chess, gardening
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, rugby, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | chess | gardening | fishing   |
| Sport   | weightlifting     | snowboarding    | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, drama, spy
3 different pets are kept: horse, cat, frog
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is between the owner of the frog and the person watching spy movies##2
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | mystery | drama |
| Pet           | cat         | horse         | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, spinach, tomato
3 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, fish
1. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person eating lemon##2
2. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | spinach | tomato | lemon |
| Pet    | hedgehog    | bird | fish     |

