.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, r&b, classical
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, golf, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | r&b  | trance  |
| Sport         | skateboarding | golf | surfing |

