.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, peach, cauliflower
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | sprite    | iced-tea      | water |
| Food       | peach | cauliflower | kiwi   |

