.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, architect, photographer
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, car
1. the photographer is on the right of the architect##1
2. the person driving the roller is the electrician##1
3. the person driving the car is the photographer##1
4. the photographer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | architect | photographer | electrician |
| Transport   | scooter | car   | roller |

