The people use 3 different means of transport: train, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the american is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the japanese##3
4. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | turkish | japanese | american |
| Transport     | car     | train   | motorbike        |

