.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, russian, pakistani
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, golf, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is the russian##1
3. the pakistani is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
