.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, drawing, dancing
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, horse
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the owner of the rat##2
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | drawing | dancing | collecting |
| Pet     | frog    | horse  | rat   |

