.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, adventure
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, gospel, reggae
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
4. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | adventure     | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | rock | reggae    |

