.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, frog, chinchilla
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, volleyball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | frog  | chinchilla   | snake |
| Sport   | rugby | volleyball | sailing       |

 